{"tid":1032571,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大師級股評人被小三控訴：「有老婆仲玩完一個又一個」","createTime":"2019-02-22T12:58:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T06:35:46.000Z","uid":31907,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"22f82806f95d81a4b8035b4a6ace0f518ca35dfc","tid":1032571,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:58:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190222/59291145\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190222%2F59291145&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLW9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=1afc155f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190222%2F59291145&h=c7a46dcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190222/59291145</a><br />\n<br />\n李華華Online】好大粒花生！股評人被小三控訴：「有老婆仲玩完一個又一個」<br />\n<br />\n12,520   <br />\n分享<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190222/large/1550828786_ae82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190222%2Flarge%2F1550828786_ae82.jpg&h=91c2dbd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該女子在FB上載多張與溫傑同遊海洋公園的照片。(翻攝M小姐facebook)<br />\n最後更新: 0222 19:18 / 建立時間 (HKT): 0222 18:17<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n恒指收市再創今年高位，但都唔及金魚缸花生指數直線飇升，皆因有位女士「M小姐」喺facebook控訴股評人溫傑「有老婆仲要玩完一個又一個」，仲貼埋佢嘅結婚證書添，嘩，真係好大粒花生。<br />\n<br />\nM小姐嘅facebook post今日喺WhatsApp瘋傳，話說2017年某日M小姐上載咗多張佢同溫傑二人同遊海洋公園嘅合照，照片尺度最盡都係搭下膊頭，不過睇得出兩人玩得好開心嘅，唔似係朋友咁簡單。<br />\n<br />\n然後，M小姐另一個post就係訴說一個絕望真相，一張結婚證書證明溫傑喺2014年結婚，唔知係咪覺得自己畀人呃咗，令自己變咗小三，佢喺個post寫住「有老婆仲要玩完一個又一個」。華華問過溫傑是不是有婚外情，佢話唔方便回應。<br />\n<br />\n事件今日喺金魚缸瘋傳後，溫傑將成個facebook page刪走，聽講M小姐同溫傑本身係同事，之前一齊出過差。呢粒花生，真係大到要啲時間消化。"},{"pid":"54cb6881bed99f5821d32ba5b06812afa1394f52","tid":1032571,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:59:03.000Z","msg":"各位有冇 m 小姐fb?"},{"pid":"f9433d60554bd88a8e83803ddae38492dcdd2b3f","tid":1032571,"uid":54337,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:07:45.000Z","msg":"條友聽都未聽過"},{"pid":"ae576cad3d280402f7bbe7db6b67663b44a2909e","tid":1032571,"uid":112308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:08:56.000Z","msg":"link呢，屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d712bd18a6a884fd9a4cb2a52e4195207bd9939f","tid":1032571,"uid":6297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:14:43.000Z","msg":"大師級只得1位！"},{"pid":"750ee7b7dee7b1eb628d99d3c3fe59d3179b9ccb","tid":1032571,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:16:24.000Z","msg":"邊撚個呀"},{"pid":"de32659369778fd261ed51017f2a78d4762cc1fd","tid":1032571,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:21:04.000Z","msg":"連小學生都蝦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c0ccae1329c3d469bbef80b54a78360f980924e","tid":1032571,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:21:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rbpxbBH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrbpxbBH.jpg&h=8fb5b8f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2b91b3a8ff7022d9332496a98f7c22301194061","tid":1032571,"uid":155784,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"d712bd18a6a884fd9a4cb2a52e4195207bd9939f","tid":1032571,"uid":6297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:14:43.000Z","msg":"大師級只得1位！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:23:10.000Z","msg":"無錯，香港衹有一個沈大師。<br />\n<br />\n沈。卓。盈。"},{"pid":"90708e29fe2ce04b2c1cebc058f143eb75e0b513","tid":1032571,"uid":77936,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:26:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bep5wDy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2